{"tid":1062150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得d本土派比人DQ都係唔抵可憐？","createTime":"2019-03-15T01:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T08:13:01.000Z","uid":138409,"like":4,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"72efafbdec0a5fb8664e48c9873d8eb0a47836a4","tid":1062150,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:51:43.000Z","msg":"本土派其實形勢上係一個弱勢嘅角色，塑造本地民族意識本身都危險，遇到共產黨基本上都比人食硬咁濟，香港政壇係咩地方所有人都知，龍蛇混雜幾多土共五毛搵藉口打壓香港自治，而呢班本土派純粹為左理想而去take risk。<br />\n<br />\n實有本土派話：「香港有司法獨立佢睇住我好安全」第一你都唔擔保個法官係100%獨立（實情亦都唔係），第二法官有權你無啊嘛，第三司法幾獨立都好總會有一次承受唔住壓力掛。<br />\n<br />\n其實本身本土派對住共產黨形勢上已經冇咩反抗能力，加上勇武冒進後遺症影響，簡直所有形式嘅組織都可以比共產黨慢慢打壓，呢種情況其實同本土派話想搞獨立，一樣係明知會有危險都去take risk,<span style=\"color: gold;\">基本上所有宣揚本土意識比人DQ嘅都係抵死唔抵可憐，自願參選但承受後果時又扮受害者</span>，呢種組織要即刻飛左佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/crkJzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/crkJzT</a>"},{"pid":"96824d2cc70486ea9e1f88b79abf8c81bbf8ec33","tid":1062150,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:52:41.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得d女去夜場飲醉比人姦都係唔抵可憐？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/crkJzT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/crkJzT</a><br />\n<br />\nReductio ad absurdum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab883f33f3b2b57adec5644c01f80ac25608705","tid":1062150,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:56:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"721e602a77bea88f5c1e09dcb0eb6ed71103c4cd","tid":1062150,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T02:01:27.000Z","msg":"無人駁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb5c6d6ad580ab420264c6583b28d5845746